.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-RENAME" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-rename \- rename a wallet directory
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-rename
.I old_name
.I new_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Renames the wallet directory
.I old_name
to
.I new_name
under
.BR WALLETS_ROOT .
Fails if the source does not exist or the destination already exists.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true}
{"ok":false,"reason":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-list (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-check (1)
